  "texts": [
    "In addition, the material that has to be provided as an explanation varies from user to user (Miller, 2019).",
    "Thirdly, our analysis also found that recommendations made via social media follow a similar pattern.",
    "As a result, the design implication may be that the user interface should be able to disseminate explanations dynamically according to the user's preferences.",
    "When the user uses the program, the dynamic delivery of explanations can include a collection choice depending on the user's preferences.",
    "When the user selects, the system can learn from that selection and create personalized explanations in the future."
